HOW TO START STREAMLIT STREAMLIT ON RASPBERRY PI4 VIA CRONTAB

Lets strat crontab:
	1. crontab -e ( now you are in crontab task planner)

Create crontab task Virlual venv:
	2. * * * * *  /home/user_name/app/bin/python3 -m streamlit run /home/user_name/streamlit/Log_in.py (it will start streamlit via venv)
	wait a minute and it will start 

Create Crontab task Conda venv:
	3.* * * * *  /home/user_name/miniforge3/bin/python3 -m streamlit run /home/user_name/streamlit/Log_in.py (will start through canda venv for me it is working  better)

# important note set time in crotab when program is starting! otherwise it will run program all the time and it will slow down your RPI4 and program 

# TO KNOW HOW TO START VENV PLEASE READ (VEN START UP)
